The paper proposes a distributed algorithm for parameter estimation in a network, which involves communication and information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), control and systems engineering (cs.SY), machine learning (cs.LG), and mathematical analysis (cs.MA). The paper also specifically mentions the application of the proposed algorithm in Cognitive Radio networks, which falls under the category of networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
